yle="line-height:1.2;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:11.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#222222;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Ich heiβe…</span><span style="font-size:11.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#222222;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">&nbsp;– My name is…</span></p></td><td style="border-left:solid #ededed 0.75pt;border-right:solid #ededed 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #ededed 0.75pt;border-top:solid #ededed 0.75pt;vertical-align:middle;background-color:#f3f3f3;padding:1.5pt 6pt 1.5pt 6pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr style="height:0pt"><td style="border-left:solid #ededed 0.75pt;border-right:solid #ededed 0.75pt;border-bottom:solid #ededed 0.75pt;border-top:solid #ededed 0.75pt;vertical-align:middle;background-color:#f3f3f3;padding:1.5pt 6pt 1.5pt 6pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:11.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#222222;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Wie heißen Sie?</span><span style="font-size:11.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#222222;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">&nbsp;– What’s your name?</span></p></td><td style="border-left:solid #ededed 0.75pt;border-right:solid #ededed 0.75pt;b